article_title: Flat Enrollment Estimates For 2016--Has The Obama Administration Given Up On Obamacare?

article_metadata.author: Robert Laszewski

og.description: Yesterday, the Obama administration said that they expect to have 10 million people enrolled on the Obamacare insurance exchanges in 2016.
